The observed behavior is that the sprite 0/BG overlap bit ($2002.D6) will not be set if the overlap occurs only on a pixel whose X screen coordinate is 255.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=9">tepples</a> — Thu Mar 24, 2005 5:24 pm</p><hr />
